item.description: Hompa Karunga, mughameni wande, mupopeli wande, ndenke ni kare ramba yakutwera nantungwedi yakuvembera. Ove mupameki ntani muna nkondo. (Source category: Rugciriku : LIKWATITO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12414)
